      <p style="font-size:15.5px;color:var(--ink-2);line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 16px;max-width:540px;">Founded in January 2018 by a team with 20-plus years at leading semiconductor makers, Powermaster designs and manufactures SiC MOSFETs and diodes, high-voltage super-junction and MV silicon MOSFETs, and IGBTs — AEC-Q101-qualified for automotive, and aimed at xEV on-board chargers and traction, server and telecom power, solar inverters and energy storage.</p>
